com.wegas.reviewing.persistence

Class Review

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.wegas.core.persistence.AbstractEntity
      • com.wegas.reviewing.persistence.Review
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Cloneable

    @Entity
public class Review
extends AbstractEntity
    A review is linked to two PeerReviewInstnace : the one who reviews and the original reviewed 'author' A review is composed of the feedback (written by reviewers) and the feedback comments (written by author). Both are a list of evaluation instances
    1. dispatched: initial state, reviewer can edit feedback
    2. reviewed: reviewer can't edit feedback anymore, author can't read feedback yet
    3. notified: author has access to the feedback and can edit feedback comments
    4. closed: feedback comments turns read-only, not yet visible by peers
    6. closed: feedback comments is visible by the reviewer
    Author:
    Maxence Laurent (maxence.laurent at gmail.com)
